author: IGN
description:
Don't miss the Launch Trailer for ARK Astraeos, a DLC for the Studio Wildcard-developed action-adventure survival game Ark: Survival Ascended developed by Nekatus and sponsored by Nitrado. Players can explore Astraeos, a breathtaking mythical world map with ever-expanding landscapes seamlessly connecting to the main clusters with official servers. The Astraeos DLC will continue to grow, with new realms, challenges, and updates shaping the world over time. ARK Astraeos is available now for PlayStation 5 (PS5), Xbox Series X|S, and PC (Steam).

#ARKAstraeos #Gaming #IGN
title: ARK Astraeos - Official Launch Trailer

author: IGN
description:
Don't miss the '#1 Movie In The World' Teaser Trailer for Captain America: Brave New World, the latest installment in the MCU from Marvel Studios. 

Captain America: Brave New World stars Anthony Mackie, Harrison Ford, Danny Ramirez, Shira Haas, Carl Lumbly, Xosha Roquemore, with Giancarlo Esposito, Liv Tyler, and Tim Blake Nelson. Marvel Studios’ Captain America: Brave New World opens in theaters on February 14, 2025.

In Captain America: Brave New World, Sam finds himself in the middle of an international incident after meeting with newly elected U.S. President Thaddeus Ross. He must discover the reason behind a nefarious global plot before the true mastermind has the entire world seeing red.

The film is directed by Julius Onah and produced by Kevin Feige and Nate Moore. Louis D’Esposito and Charles Newirth serve as executive producers. The screenplay is by Rob Edwards and Malcolm Spellman & Dalan Musso and Julius Onah & Peter Glanz, with story by Rob Edwards and Malcolm Spellman
title: Captain America: Brave New World - Official '#1 Movie In The World' Teaser Trailer (2025)

author: IGN
description:
Avowed is shaping up to be one of Xbox’s biggest RPGs, but does its reveal make you more excited for The Outer Worlds 2? In this discussion, we break down Avowed’s gameplay, world, and RPG mechanics while comparing its potential impact on Obsidian’s other major project. Will Avowed set the stage for an even bigger Outer Worlds sequel? Let us know your thoughts in the comments!

For more on the Series X Price and Xbox News, cmake sure to check out IGN's Podcast Unlocked on IGN.com and youtube.com/igngames
title: Does Avowed Boost Excitement for Outer Worlds 2? - Unlocked Clips

author: IGN
description:
Sony’s PC release strategy has been heavily led by Insomniac and Nixxes, with Spider-Man 2 being Sony’s quickest PlayStation to PC release yet. Has that rapid pace impacted the quality of the port? We test a range of PC hardware against the PS5 Pro to see how much higher the game can scale, how it runs, and if this is the premium way to play this superhero adventure. Graphics, performance, patche,s and spider webs are all covered in our IGN Spiderman 2 PC performance review.


0:00 Introduction
0:23 PC improvements, settings, and comparisons to PS5 Pro
3:40 The challenges of the PC port and issues across the platform
6:00 Performance testing RTX5090/7950X3D vs PS5 Pro
7:55 RTX4090/5800X3D performance testing
8:58 RX6800/5600X performance testing and bigger issues
10:15 RTX2070/2700 performance testing
11:20 RTX4050/i12650H Laptop & Steam Deck performance testing
12:21 The main issues and bugs with the port right now
14:38 Summary

#SpiderMan2 #Gaming #IGN
title: Spider-Man 2: PC vs PS5 Pro vs PS5 Performance Review

description:
Become a pilot in the world of Mobile Suit Gundam SEED. Watch the Mobile Suit Gundam SEED: Battle Destiny Remastered announcement trailer to learn about the features of the remaster of this action game, which is available for the first time with English localization. In Mobile Suit Gundam SEED: Battle Destiny Remastered, engage in action-packed Gundam battles, complete missions, and tune up your newly acquired Mobile Suits. Mobile Suit Gundam SEED: Battle Destiny Remastered will be available on Nintendo Switch and PC on May 22, 2025.
